	<div id="CL">
	<h2> Cube Maintenance:</h2>
	<p>Depending on usage and determination to get faster,
	its important and best to in my opinion,<br>to clean your cubes
	inner parts once a month with a towel and water and lubricate
	your cube once week. <br>
	YouTube Video on:<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k5oSkyyzrHU">Cube Lubrication</a>
	
	
